The Summoning is a side quest in Sal's campaign with a focus on Negotiation.

== Description ==
An [[Guard]] needs you to deliver an [[Admiralty]] summons to a [[Spree]] [[Thug]]. He isn't going to take it willingly.

== Rewards ==

* Starting Bonus
* 55 shills
* Get an [[Items|Item Card]]

